#: src/fsearch.c:883
msgid ""
"For command-line search help, run: fsearch --cli --help\n"
"For shared configuration help, run: fsearch config --help"
msgstr ""
"Le haghaidh cabhair chuardaigh ar líne na n-orduithe, rith: fsearch --cli --help\n"
"Le haghaidh cabhair chumraíochta roinnte, rith: fsearch config --help"

#: src/fsearch_cli.c:181
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch --cli [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Search the existing FSearch index and print matching paths.\n"
"\n"
"  -s, --search PATTERN       Search with FSearch query syntax\n"
"      --path DIRECTORY        Search recursively below DIRECTORY (default: current directory)\n"
"      --global                Search every indexed location\n"
"      --limit COUNT          Print at most COUNT results\n"
"      --unlimit, --unlimited Print every result\n"
"  -u, --update-database      Rescan the configured index and exit\n"
"      --about                Print one-line build information\n"
"  -h, --help                 Show this help\n"
"\n"
"Configuration: fsearch config --help\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search invoice              # current directory\n"
"  fsearch --cli --path ~/Documents --search invoice\n"
"  fsearch --cli --global --search invoice\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'file:size:>20mb'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'ext:jpg;png'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'path:projects report'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'report AND ext:pdf'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search '(draft OR final) !archive'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'file:regex:\".+\\.pdf$\"'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'case:AGENTS'        # case-sensitive\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'case:regex:\"^AGENTS\\.md$\"'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'glob:**/*.png'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'path:glob:**/AGENTS.md'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'case:glob:AGENTS.md' # case-sensitive glob\n"
"\n"
"Examples use space as AND. Try file:, folder:, path:, ext:, size:, dm:, case:, regex:, and glob:.\n"
"Boolean syntax: AND or &&; OR or ||; NOT or !. Parentheses group terms.\n"
"Glob syntax: * excludes /; ** spans directories; ? matches one character; [a-c] is a range;\n"
"Glob searches paths by default; use **/ for any depth; file:glob: searches file names.\n"
"{png,jpg} selects alternatives; {01..12} is an inclusive numeric range; \\* matches a literal *.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch --cli [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Cuardaigh an t-innéacs FSearch atá ann cheana agus taispeáin na conairí meaitseála.\n"
"\n"
"  -s, --search PATTERN       Cuardaigh le comhréir iarratais FSearch\n"
"      --path DIRECTORY        Cuardaigh go hathchúrsach faoi DIRECTORY (réamhshocrú: eolaire reatha)\n"
"      --global                Cuardaigh gach suíomh innéacsaithe\n"
"      --limit COUNT          Taispeáin ar a mhéad COUNT toradh\n"
"      --unlimit, --unlimited Taispeáin gach toradh\n"
"  -u, --update-database      Athscan an t-innéacs cumraithe agus scoir\n"
"      --about                Taispeáin faisnéis tógála aon líne\n"
"  -h, --help                 Taispeáin an chabhair seo\n"
"\n"
"Cumraíocht: fsearch config --help\n"
"\n"
"Samplaí:\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search invoice              # eolaire reatha\n"
"  fsearch --cli --path ~/Documents --search invoice\n"
"  fsearch --cli --global --search invoice\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'file:size:>20mb'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'ext:jpg;png'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'path:projects report'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'report AND ext:pdf'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search '(draft OR final) !archive'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'file:regex:\".+\\.pdf$\"'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'case:AGENTS'        # cás-íogair\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'case:regex:\"^AGENTS\\.md$\"'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'glob:**/*.png'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'path:glob:**/AGENTS.md'\n"
"  fsearch --cli --search 'case:glob:AGENTS.md' # glob cás-íogair\n"
"\n"
"Úsáideann na samplaí spás mar AND. Bain triail as file:, folder:, path:, ext:, size:, dm:, case:, regex:, agus glob:.\n"
"Comhréir Bhúlach: AND nó &&; OR nó ||; NOT nó !. Grúpálann lúibíní téarmaí.\n"
"Comhréir glob: fágann * an / as; réimníonn ** eolairí; meaitseálann ? carachtar amháin; is raon é [a-c];\n"
"Cuardaíonn glob conairí de réir réamhshocraithe; úsáid **/ le haghaidh doimhneacht ar bith; cuardaíonn file:glob: ainmneacha comhad.\n"
"roghnaíonn {png,jpg} malairtí; {01..12} is raon uimhriúil cuimsitheach é; \\* comhoiriúnaíonn le réalta liteartha *.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:111
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config COMMAND [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"View and modify the shared FSearch GUI and CLI configuration.\n"
"\n"
"Configuration commands:\n"
"  path                         Print the configuration file path\n"
"  show [SECTION] [--json]      Show settings\n"
"  get KEY [--json]             Print one scalar setting\n"
"  set KEY VALUE                Set one scalar setting\n"
"  unset KEY                    Restore one scalar setting default\n"
"  reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"                               Restore defaults\n"
"  doctor                       Check configuration and index consistency\n"
"  roots list|add|set|remove    Manage indexed roots\n"
"  excludes list|add|remove|hidden\n"
"                               Manage index exclusions\n"
"  filters list|add|set|remove|reset\n"
"                               Manage saved search filters\n"
"\n"
"Scalar values use true/false, decimal integers, or strings.\n"
"Run 'fsearch config show' to list every scalar key and current value.\n"
"Scalar sections: search, application, window, ui, columns, sort, dialogs.\n"
"Use 'fsearch config roots|excludes|filters --help' for family options.\n"
"Close the FSearch GUI before changing shared settings.\n"
"Index changes become searchable on the next CLI search, or immediately with --rescan.\n"
"Use --json with show, get, and collection list commands.\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  fsearch config show search --json\n"
"  fsearch config get search.match-case\n"
"  fsearch config set search.match-case true\n"
"  fsearch config roots add ~/Code --monitor --one-file-system --rescan\n"
"  fsearch config excludes add '*.tmp' --type wildcard --scope basename --target files\n"
"  fsearch config filters add Documents --query 'ext:pdf' --macro docs\n"
"  fsearch config reset search --yes\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config COMMAND [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Féach ar an gcumraíocht chomhroinnte GUI agus CLI FSearch agus mionathraigh í.\n"
"\n"
"Orduithe cumraíochta:\n"
"  path                         Taispeáin conair an chomhaid chumraíochta\n"
"  show [SECTION] [--json]      Taispeáin socruithe\n"
"  get KEY [--json]             Taispeáin socrú scálach amháin\n"
"  set KEY VALUE                Socraigh socrú scálach amháin\n"
"  unset KEY                    Athchóirigh réamhshocrú socraithe scálach amháin\n"
"  reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"                               Athchóirigh réamhshocruithe\n"
"  doctor                       Seiceáil comhsheasmhacht na cumraíochta agus an innéacs\n"
"  roots list|add|set|remove    Bainistigh fréamhacha innéacsaithe\n"
"  excludes list|add|remove|hidden\n"
"                               Bainistigh eisiaimh innéacs\n"
"  filters list|add|set|remove|reset\n"
"                               Bainistigh scagairí cuardaigh sábháilte\n"
"\n"
"Úsáideann luachanna scálacha true/false, slánuimhreacha deachúlacha, nó teaghráin.\n"
"Rith 'fsearch config show' chun gach eochair scálach agus a luach reatha a liostú.\n"
"Rannáin scálacha: search, application, window, ui, columns, sort, dialogs.\n"
"Úsáid 'fsearch config roots|excludes|filters --help' le haghaidh roghanna teaghlaigh.\n"
"Dún GUI FSearch sula n-athraíonn tú socruithe comhroinnte.\n"
"Bíonn athruithe innéacs inchuardaithe ar an gcéad chuardach CLI eile, nó láithreach le --rescan.\n"
"Úsáid --json leis na horduithe show, get, agus collection list.\n"
"\n"
"Samplaí:\n"
"  fsearch config show search --json\n"
"  fsearch config get search.match-case\n"
"  fsearch config set search.match-case true\n"
"  fsearch config roots add ~/Code --monitor --one-file-system --rescan\n"
"  fsearch config excludes add '*.tmp' --type wildcard --scope basename --target files\n"
"  fsearch config filters add Documents --query 'ext:pdf' --macro docs\n"
"  fsearch config reset search --yes\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:152
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config show [SECTION] [--json]\n"
"Show all scalar settings or one dotted section.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config show [SECTION] [--json]\n"
"Taispeáin gach socrú scálach nó rannán poncaithe amháin.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:154
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config get KEY [--json]\n"
"Print one typed scalar value. Discover keys with 'fsearch config show'.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config get KEY [--json]\n"
"Taispeáin luach scálach clóscríofa amháin. Aimsigh eochracha le 'fsearch config show'.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:157
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config set KEY VALUE\n"
"Set a boolean, integer, string, or enumerated scalar value.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config set KEY VALUE\n"
"Socraigh luach scálach Boole, slánuimhir, teaghrán, nó áirithe.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:159
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config unset KEY\n"
"Restore one scalar setting to its built-in default.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config unset KEY\n"
"Athchóirigh socrú scálach amháin chuig a réamhshocrú ionsuite.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:161
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"Reset is destructive and requires --yes. --rescan applies to roots, database, excludes, or all.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"Tá reset millteach agus éilíonn sé --yes. Baineann --rescan le roots, database, excludes, nó all.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:164
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config doctor\n"
"Check configuration readability and whether the saved index uses the same roots and exclusions.\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config doctor\n"
"Seiceáil inléiteacht na cumraíochta agus an úsáideann an t-innéacs sábháilte na fréamhacha agus na heisiaimh chéanna.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:170
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config roots COMMAND [PATH] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  list [--json]                List indexed roots\n"
"  add PATH [OPTIONS]           Add a root directory\n"
"  set PATH [OPTIONS]           Change an existing root\n"
"  remove PATH [--rescan]       Remove an existing root\n"
"\n"
"Options for add and set:\n"
"  --active, --inactive\n"
"  --monitor, --no-monitor\n"
"  --one-file-system, --no-one-file-system\n"
"  --scan-after-launch, --no-scan-after-launch\n"
"  --rescan-every SECONDS        Set periodic rescan interval; 0 disables it\n"
"  --rescan                      Rebuild the index immediately after saving\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config roots COMMAND [PATH] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Orduithe:\n"
"  list [--json]                Liostaigh fréamhacha innéacsaithe\n"
"  add PATH [OPTIONS]           Cuir eolaire fréimhe leis\n"
"  set PATH [OPTIONS]           Athraigh fréamh atá ann cheana\n"
"  remove PATH [--rescan]       Bain fréamh atá ann cheana\n"
"\n"
"Roghanna le haghaidh add agus set:\n"
"  --active, --inactive\n"
"  --monitor, --no-monitor\n"
"  --one-file-system, --no-one-file-system\n"
"  --scan-after-launch, --no-scan-after-launch\n"
"  --rescan-every SECONDS        Socraigh eatramh athscanta tréimhsiúil; díchumasaíonn 0 é\n"
"  --rescan                      Atóg an t-innéacs láithreach tar éis a shábháil\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:187
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config excludes COMMAND [PATTERN|VALUE] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  list [--json]                 List exclusions\n"
"  add PATTERN [OPTIONS]         Add an exclusion\n"
"  remove PATTERN [OPTIONS]      Remove a matching exclusion\n"
"  hidden [true|false] [--rescan]\n"
"                                View or change hidden-file exclusion\n"
"\n"
"Options for add and remove:\n"
"  --type fixed|wildcard|regex   Default: fixed\n"
"  --scope full-path|basename    Default: full-path\n"
"  --target both|files|folders   Default: both\n"
"  --active, --inactive          Add state or removal selector\n"
"  --rescan                      Rebuild the index immediately after saving\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config excludes COMMAND [PATTERN|VALUE] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Orduithe:\n"
"  list [--json]                 Liostaigh eisiaimh\n"
"  add PATTERN [OPTIONS]         Cuir eisiamh leis\n"
"  remove PATTERN [OPTIONS]      Bain eisiamh meaitseála\n"
"  hidden [true|false] [--rescan]\n"
"                                Féach ar nó athraigh eisiamh comhad folaithe\n"
"\n"
"Roghanna le haghaidh add agus remove:\n"
"  --type fixed|wildcard|regex   Réamhshocrú: fixed\n"
"  --scope full-path|basename    Réamhshocrú: full-path\n"
"  --target both|files|folders   Réamhshocrú: both\n"
"  --active, --inactive          Roghnóir stádais cuir-leis nó bainte\n"
"  --rescan                      Atóg an t-innéacs láithreach tar éis a shábháil\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:204
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config filters COMMAND [NAME] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  list [--json]                 List saved filters\n"
"  add NAME [OPTIONS]            Add a named filter\n"
"  set NAME [OPTIONS]            Change a named filter\n"
"  remove NAME                   Remove a named filter\n"
"  reset                         Restore built-in filters\n"
"\n"
"Options for add and set:\n"
"  --query QUERY                 Saved FSearch query\n"
"  --macro MACRO                 Query macro name\n"
"  --case, --no-case             Match case\n"
"  --path, --no-path             Search full paths\n"
"  --regex, --no-regex           Treat query as a regular expression\n"
msgstr ""
"Úsáid: fsearch config filters COMMAND [NAME] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Orduithe:\n"
"  list [--json]                 Liostaigh scagairí sábháilte\n"
"  add NAME [OPTIONS]            Cuir scagaire ainmnithe leis\n"
"  set NAME [OPTIONS]            Athraigh scagaire ainmnithe\n"
"  remove NAME                   Bain scagaire ainmnithe\n"
"  reset                         Athchóirigh scagairí ionsuite\n"
"\n"
"Roghanna le haghaidh add agus set:\n"
"  --query QUERY                 Iarratas FSearch sábháilte\n"
"  --macro MACRO                 Ainm macra an iarratais\n"
"  --case, --no-case             Meaitseáil cás\n"
"  --path, --no-path             Cuardaigh conairí iomlána\n"
"  --regex, --no-regex           Caith leis an iarratas mar shlonn rialta\n"

