#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:855
msgid ""
"<b>Enable dark theme:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the system theme is asked to use a darker styling for the application <i>(i.e. dark UI elements on bright text)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Note that not all system themes provide such a darker variant, therefore enabling this setting might not have an effect."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cumasaigh téama dorcha:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, iarrtar ar théama an chórais stíleáil níos dorcha a úsáid don fheidhmchlár <i>(i.e. eilimintí dorcha Chomhéadain ar théacs geal)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara nach soláthraíonn gach téama córais a leithéid de leagan níos dorcha, agus mar sin seans nach mbeadh éifeacht ag cumasú an tsocraithe seo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:873
msgid ""
"<b>Enable client-side decorations:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search entry and main menu are displayed in the window title bar.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the main menu is displayed as a menu bar with the search entry below it.\n"
"This resembles a more traditional UI layout and takes a little bit more space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cumasaigh maisiúcháin ar thaobh an chliaint:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeántar an iontráil chuardaigh agus an príomh-roghchlár i mbarra teidil na fuinneoige.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé díchumasaithe, taispeántar an príomh-roghchlár mar bharra roghchláir leis an iontráil chuardaigh thíos ann.\n"
"Tá sé seo cosúil le leagan amach Chomhéadain níos traidisiúnta agus tógann sé beagán níos mó spáis."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:893
msgid ""
"<b>Use binary units instead of decimal units:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This settings controls how file sizes are displayed.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binary units:</b> This refers to binary IEC prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 KiB = 1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimal  units:</b> This refers to decimal SI prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 kB = 1000 bytes)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Úsáid aonaid dhénártha in ionad na n-aonad deachúil:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Rialaíonn an socrú seo conas a léirítear méideanna comhaid.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Aonaid dhénártha:</b> Tagraíonn sé seo do réimíreanna dénártha <i> (m.sh. 1 KiB = 1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Aonaid dheachúla:</b> Tagraíonn sé seo do réimíreanna deachúla SI <i>(m.sh. 1 kB = 1000 beart)</i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:913
msgid ""
"<b>Remember window size:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the window size from the previous session will be restored when you open an FSearch window.\n"
"\n"
"Note that some window managers ignore this request and force the window to have a different size."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuimhnigh méid na fuinneoige:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar méid na fuinneoige ón seisiún roimhe seo a athbhunú nuair a osclaíonn tú fuinneog FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara go ndéanann roinnt bainisteoirí fuinneoige neamhaird den iarratas seo agus go gcuireann siad iallach ar an bhfuinneog méid difriúil a bheith aici."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:932
msgid ""
"<b>Behaviour after successfully opening a file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"When a file/folder was successfully opened one of the following actions can be performed:\n"
"\t• <b>Nothing:</b> Nothing happens.\n"
"                        • <b>Minimize:</b> The currently selected FSearch window becomes minimized.\n"
"\t• <b>Close:</b> Quit FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure if those actions should be triggered when the file was opened with\n"
"\t• <b>keyboard shortcuts or menu entries</b> and/or\n"
"\t• <b>mouse click</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Iompar tar éis comhad a oscailt go rathúil:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Nuair a osclaíodh comhad/fillteán go rathúil is féidir ceann de na gníomhartha seo a leanas a dhéanamh:\n"
"\t• <b>Tada:</b> Ní tharlaíonn tada.\n"
"                        • <b>Íoslaghdaigh:</b> Íoslaghdaítear an fhuinneog FSearch atá roghnaithe faoi láthair.\n"
"\t• <b>Dún:</b> Scoir FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat a chumrú ar cheart na gníomhartha sin a chur i ngníomh nuair a osclaíodh an comhad leis\n"
"\t• <b>aicearraí méarchláir nó iontrálacha roghchláir</b> agus/nó\n"
"\t• <b>cliceáil luiche</b>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:956
msgid ""
"<b>Show highlighted search terms:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search terms will be highlighted in the results view. For example when you search for \"foo\" all appearances of <i>foo</i> in file/folder names will be highlighted with bold characters:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"This also works for regular expressions and wildcard expressions starting or ending with an asterisk. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin téarmaí cuardaigh aibhsithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, cuirfear béim ar na téarmaí cuardaigh i radharc na dtorthaí. Mar shampla, nuair a chuardaíonn tú \\\"foo\\\" léireofar gach láithriú <i>foo</i> in ainmneacha comhaid/fillteán le carachtair throma:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tcomhad.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"Oibríonn sé seo freisin le haghaidh slonn rialta agus slonn saoróg ag tosú nó ag críochnú le réiltín."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:978
msgid ""
"<b>Show tooltips:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the results view will show the full path of the focused file/folder in a small tooltip window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin leideanna uirlisí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, léireoidh amharc na dtorthaí conair iomlán an chomhaid/fhillteáin dhírithe i bhfuinneog bheag leideanna."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:995
msgid ""
"<b>Show icons in name column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, file/folder icons will be shown in the name column."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin deilbhíní sa cholún ainm:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeánfar deilbhíní comhaid/fillteán sa cholún ainm."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1012
msgid ""
"<b>Remember column configuration:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the column configuration of the results view from the previous session will be restored when you open an FSearch window. This includes the size and visibility of all columns."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuimhnigh cumraíocht an cholúin:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar cumraíocht an cholúin d’amharc na dtorthaí ón seisiún roimhe seo a athchóiriú nuair a osclaíonn tú fuinneog FSearch. Áirítear leis seo méid agus infheictheacht na gcolún go léir."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1029
msgid ""
"<b>Remember sort order:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the sort order of the results view from the previous session will be restored when you open an FSearch window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuimhnigh an t-ord sórtála:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar ord sórtála radharc na dtorthaí ón seisiún roimhe seo a athchóiriú nuair a osclaíonn tú fuinneog FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1046
msgid ""
"<b>Open path with double click in path column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, double clicking in the path column will open the selected path."
msgstr ""
"<b>Oscail conair le cliceáil faoi dhó sa cholún conaire:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar an conair roghnaithe a oscailt trí chliceáil faoi dhó sa cholún conaire."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1063
msgid ""
"<b>Single click to open:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a single click will open the selected file/folder. If you only want to select a file/folder while this setting is active, you need to hold <i>Ctrl</i> at the same time while clicking the file/folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cliceáil amháin le hoscailt:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, osclóidh cliceáil amháin an comhad/fillteán roghnaithe. Mura dteastaíonn uait ach comhad/fillteán a roghnú agus an socrú seo gníomhach, ní mór duit <i>Ctrl</i> a choinneáil ag an am céanna agus cliceáil ar an gcomhad/fillteán."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1080
msgid ""
"<b>Show database indexing status:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the path that is currently being indexed is displayed in the statusbar."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin stádas innéacsaithe an bhunachair shonraí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeántar an chonair atá á hinnéacsú faoi láthair sa bharra stádais."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1097
msgid ""
"<b>Show warning dialogs:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a warning dialog is displayed when a file or folder failed to open."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin dialóga rabhaidh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeántar dialóg rabhaidh nuair a theip ar chomhad nó ar fhillteán a oscailt."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1114
msgid ""
"<b>Search in path when query contains path separators:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing path separators (i.e. \"/\") will be automatically matched against the full path of a file or folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuardaigh sa chonair nuair atá deighilteoirí conaire sa cheist:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar téarmaí cuardaigh ina bhfuil deighilteoirí conaire (i.e. \\\"/\\\") a mheaitseáil go huathoibríoch le conair iomlán comhaid nó fillteáin."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1131
msgid ""
"<b>Match case when query contains at least one upper case character:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing at least one upper case character will trigger a case-sensitive search. This means a search term like <i>Foo</i> will match <i>FooBar.txt</i> but not <i>foobar.txt</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Meaitseálann an cás nuair atá carachtar cás uachtair amháin ar a laghad sa cheist:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, cuirfidh téarmaí cuardaigh ina bhfuil ar a laghad carachtar cás uachtair amháin tús le cuardach cás-íogair. Ciallaíonn sé seo go mbeidh téarma cuardaigh cosúil le <i>Foo</i> ag teacht le <i>FooBar.txt</i> ach nach mbeidh <i>foobar.txt</i> ann."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1148
msgid ""
"<b>Hide results when search is empty:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, no search results are displayed when the search entry is empty.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, all files and folders will be displayed when the search entry is empty."
msgstr ""
"<b>Folaigh na torthaí nuair atá an cuardach folamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, ní thaispeántar torthaí cuardaigh nuair a bhíonn an iontráil chuardaigh folamh.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé díchumasaithe, taispeánfar gach comhad agus fillteán nuair a bhíonn an iontráil chuardaigh folamh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1167
msgid ""
"<b>Search as you type:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search is automatically updated with every keystroke.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the search is only updated when you hit <i>Enter</i> or press the search button. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuardaigh agus tú ag clóscríobh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déantar an cuardach a nuashonrú go huathoibríoch le gach eochairbhuillí.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé díchumasaithe, ní dhéantar an cuardach a nuashonrú ach amháin nuair a bhuaileann tú <i>Iontráil</i> nó nuair a bhrúnn tú an cnaipe cuardaigh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1186
msgid ""
"<b>Update database on start:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the database will be updated automatically in the background when you start FSearch."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuashonraigh an bunachar sonraí nuair a thosóidh tú:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar an bunachar sonraí a nuashonrú go huathoibríoch sa chúlra nuair a thosaíonn tú ar FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1203
msgid ""
"<b>Included folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains all folders you want to include in the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the path will included in the database to be searched in.\n"
"\t• <b>Path:</b> The full path to be included.\n"
"\t• <b>One Filesystem:</b> If enabled, FSearch won't cross filesystem boundaries for this folder"
msgstr ""
"<b>Fillteáin san áireamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ar an liosta seo tá gach fillteán is mian leat a chur san áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Gníomhach:</b> Má tá sé cumasaithe, cuirfear an chonair san áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí a mbeidh tú ag cuardach ann.\n"
"\t• <b>Conair:</b> An chonair iomlán le cur san áireamh.\n"
"\t• <b>Córas Comhad amháin:</b> Má tá sé cumasaithe, ní thrasnóidh FSearch teorainneacha an chórais comhad don fhillteán seo"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1224
msgid ""
"<b>Add folder to database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can select a folder you want to include in the database for searching."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir fillteán leis an mbunachar sonraí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo dialóg inar féidir leat fillteán a roghnú is mian leat a áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí lena chuardach."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1241
msgid ""
"<b>Add a specific path:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Type the full path of a folder here and click the button next to it to include that folder in the database. This is useful for adding a path directly without browsing for it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir conair ar leith leis:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Clóscríobh conair iomlán an fhillteáin anseo agus cliceáil ar an gcnaipe in aice leis chun an fillteán sin a chur san áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí. Tá sé seo úsáideach chun conair a chur leis go díreach gan brabhsáil dó."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1258
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected folder from the list of included folders."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bain an ró roghnaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Baineann sé seo an fillteán roghnaithe as liosta na bhfillteán atá san áireamh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1275
msgid ""
"<b>Attempt to monitor:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch watches this folder for changes and keeps the database up to date automatically, so you don't have to rescan manually.\n"
"\n"
"Monitoring isn't supported on every file system and uses a small amount of system resources per watched folder. For large directory trees with many files the system may run out of resources to watch them all."
msgstr ""
"<b>Déan iarracht monatóireacht a dhéanamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, féachann FSearch ar an bhfillteán seo le haghaidh athruithe agus coinníonn sé an bunachar sonraí cothrom le dáta go huathoibríoch, mar sin ní gá duit a athscanadh de láimh.\n"
"\n"
"Ní thacaítear le monatóireacht ar gach córas comhaid agus úsáideann sé méid beag acmhainní córais in aghaidh an fhillteáin faire. I gcás crann eolaire mór le go leor comhad d'fhéadfadh an córas rith as acmhainní chun féachaint orthu go léir."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1294
msgid ""
"<b>Scan after launch:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned every time FSearch starts, so the database reflects any changes made while FSearch wasn't running."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scan tar éis an tseolta:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déantar an fillteán seo a athscanadh gach uair a thosaíonn FSearch, mar sin léiríonn an bunachar sonraí aon athruithe a rinneadh nuair nach raibh FSearch ag rith."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1311
msgid ""
"<b>Stay on one file system:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch won't cross file system boundaries while scanning this folder. Mounted file systems below it (e.g. external drives or network shares) are skipped."
msgstr ""
"<b>Fan ar chóras comhad amháin:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, ní thrasnóidh FSearch teorainneacha an chórais comhad agus an fillteán seo á scanadh. Ní dhéantar córais comhad suite faoina bhun (m.sh. tiomántáin sheachtracha nó scaireanna líonra)."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1328
msgid ""
"<b>Rescan every:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned automatically at the given interval. Use the hours and minutes fields to set how often the rescan happens.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful for folders on file systems that can't be monitored for changes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Athscan gach:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar an fillteán seo a athscanadh go huathoibríoch ag an eatramh a thugtar. Bain úsáid as na réimsí uaireanta agus miontuairiscí chun cé chomh minic a tharlaíonn an t-athscanadh a shocrú.\n"
"\n"
"Tá sé seo úsáideach le haghaidh fillteáin ar chórais comhad nach féidir monatóireacht a dhéanamh orthu le haghaidh athruithe."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1347
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains rules for the files and folders you want to exclude from the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the rule is applied and matching items are excluded.\n"
"\t• <b>Pattern:</b> The text matched against each item, interpreted according to the Type.\n"
"\t• <b>Type:</b> How the pattern is interpreted — <i>Literal</i> (exact text), <i>Wildcard</i> (using * and ?) or <i>Regex</i> (a regular expression).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Whether the pattern is matched against the item's <i>Full Path</i> or only its <i>Basename</i> (the name without the path).\n"
"\t• <b>Applies To:</b> Whether the rule affects <i>Files</i>, <i>Folders</i> or both."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rialacha eisiaimh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tá rialacha sa liosta seo maidir leis na comhaid agus na fillteáin is mian leat a eisiamh ón mbunachar sonraí.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Gníomhach:</b> Má tá sé cumasaithe, cuirtear an riail i bhfeidhm agus fágtar míreanna meaitseála as an áireamh.\n"
"\t• <b>Patrún:</b> An téacs a mheaitseáil le gach mír, léirmhínithe de réir an Chineáil.\n"
"\t• <b>Cineál:</b> Conas a dhéantar an patrún a léirmhíniú — <i>Litiriúil</i> (téacs cruinn), <i>Saoróg</i> (ag úsáid * agus ?) nó <i>Regex</i> (slonn rialta).\n"
"\t• <b>Meaitseáil:</b> Cibé an bhfuil an patrún meaitseáilte le <i>Conair Iomlán</i> na míre nó lena <i>Bunainm</i> amháin (an t-ainm gan an chonair).\n"
"\t• <b>Baineann sé le:</b> Cibé an mbíonn tionchar ag an riail ar <i>Comhaid</i>, <i>Fillteáin</i> nó an dá rud."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1370
msgid ""
"<b>Add exclude rule:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This adds a new, empty rule to the list. Edit its Pattern, Type, Match and Applies To columns to control what gets excluded from the database."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir riail eisiaimh leis:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Cuireann sé seo riail nua, folamh leis an liosta. Cuir a Phatrún, Cineál, Meaitseáil agus Feidhmíonn Le Colúin in Eagar chun a bhfuil eisiata ón mbunachar sonraí a rialú."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1387
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected rule from the list of exclude rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bain an ró roghnaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Baineann sé seo an riail roghnaithe as liosta na rialacha eisiata."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1404
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default set of exclude rules.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All rules which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Aischuir na rialacha eisiata réamhshocraithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Athshocróidh an cnaipe seo an tacar réamhshocraithe rialacha eisiata.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Caillfear gach riail a chruthaigh nó a chuir an t-úsáideoir in eagar! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1423
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude files and folders from database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a semi-colon separated list of files (or folders) you want to exclude from the database. For example <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> will exclude all files or folders which are called either <i>.git</i> or <i>.cache</i> or end with <i>.swp</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Eisiaigh comhaid agus fillteáin ón mbunachar sonraí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Seo liosta leathchoilín de chomhaid (nó fillteáin) ar mhaith leat a eisiamh ón mbunachar sonraí. Mar shampla ní dhéanfaidh <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> gach comhad nó fillteán ar a dtugtar <i>.git</i> nó <i>.cache</i> nó a chríochnaíonn le <i>.swp</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1440
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude hidden files and folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, hidden files and folders will be excluded from the database <i>(i.e. all files or folders which start with a dot character)</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Eisiaigh comhaid fholaithe agus fillteáin:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, fágfar comhaid fholaithe agus fillteáin as an áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí <i> (i.e. gach comhad nó fillteán a thosaíonn le carachtar ponc)</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1470
msgid ""
"<b>Periodically update database at a specific time interval:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled and as long as FSearch is running, the database will be updated periodically with the given time interval.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to update the database in the background, even when FSearch is not running, you should use tools like cron or systemd timers to periodically trigger the update with:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuashonraigh an bunachar sonraí go tréimhsiúil ag eatramh ama ar leith:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe agus fad atá FSearch ar siúl, déanfar an bunachar sonraí a nuashonrú go tréimhsiúil leis an eatramh ama tugtha.\n"
"\n"
"Más mian leat an bunachar sonraí sa chúlra a nuashonrú, fiú nuair nach bhfuil FSearch ag rith, ba cheart duit uirlisí amhail amadóirí cron nó córas a úsáid chun an nuashonrú a spreagadh go tréimhsiúil le:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1491
msgid ""
"<b>Launch desktop files:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, activating a <i>.desktop</i> file will launch the application defined within that file. This way FSearch can act like an application launcher. Otherwise the <i>.desktop</i> file will be opened with the default handler for this type of files, which is usually a text editor."
msgstr ""
"<b>Seol comhaid deisce:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, má ghníomhachtaítear comhad <i>.desktop</i> seolfar an feidhmchlár atá sainithe laistigh den chomhad sin. Ar an mbealach seo is féidir le FSearch gníomhú ar nós tosaitheoir feidhmchlár. Seachas sin osclófar an comhad <i>.desktop</i> leis an láimhseálaí réamhshocraithe don chineál seo comhaid, ar gnátheagarthóir téacs é."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1508
msgid ""
"<b>Filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a list of all available filters. A filter is a predefined search.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Name:</b> A unique and descriptive identifier for the filter\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> By typing the macro text followed by a ':' you can enable the filter on demand\n"
"\t• <b>Query:</b> The search term by which the database should be filtered"
msgstr ""
"<b>Scagairí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Seo liosta de na scagairí go léir atá ar fáil. Is cuardach réamhshainithe é scagaire.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Ainm:</b> Aitheantóir uathúil agus tuairisciúil don scagaire\n"
"\t• <b>Macra:</b> Trí an macra-théacs a chlóscríobh agus ':' ina dhiaidh is féidir leat an scagaire a chumasú ar éileamh\n"
"\t• <b>Ceist:</b> An téarma cuardaigh faoinar cheart an bunachar sonraí a scagadh"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1529
msgid ""
"<b>Add a new filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit a new filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir scagaire nua leis:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo dialóg inar féidir leat scagaire nua a chur in eagar."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1546
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button removes the currently selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bain an scagaire roghnaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Baineann an cnaipe seo amach an scagaire atá roghnaithe faoi láthair."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1563
msgid ""
"<b>Edit selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit the selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir an scagaire roghnaithe in eagar:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo dialóg inar féidir leat an scagaire roghnaithe a chur in eagar."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1580
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default filter configuration.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All filters which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Aischuir na scagairí réamhshocraithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Athshocróidh an cnaipe seo cumraíocht réamhshocraithe an scagaire.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Caillfear gach scagaire a chruthaigh nó a chuir an t-úsáideoir in eagar! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1599
msgid ""
"<b>Exit on Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch exits when the Escape key is pressed instead of the window being minimized."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scoir ar Éalú:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, scoireann FSearch nuair a bhrúitear an eochair Escape in ionad an fhuinneog a íoslaghdú."

#: src/fsearch_statusbar.ui:407
msgid ""
"Search term contains upper case characters.\n"
"<b>Match Case</b> was temporarily activated for this term."
msgstr ""
"Tá carachtair chás uachtair sa téarma cuardaigh.\n"
"Cuireadh <b>Match Case</b> i ngníomh go sealadach don téarma seo."

#: src/fsearch_statusbar.ui:514
msgid ""
"Search term contains path separators.\n"
"<b>Search in Path</b> was temporarily activated for this term."
msgstr ""
"Tá deighilteoirí conaire sa téarma cuardaigh.\n"
"Cuireadh <b>Search in Path</b> i ngníomh go sealadach don téarma seo."

#: src/fsearch_statusbar.ui:726
msgid ""
"The search was cancelled before it finished.\n"
"<b>These results are incomplete.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Cuireadh an cuardach ar ceal sular chríochnaigh sé.\n"
"<b>Tá na torthaí seo neamhiomlán.</b>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:163
msgid ""
"You can now actively watch individual folders to eliminate frequent rescans. File changes then appear in your search results immediately.\n"
"\n"
"To enable this feature go to the Database section of the Preferences dialog.\n"
"\n"
"See the online documentation for more information:\n"
"<a href=\"URL\">https://github.com/cboxdoerfer/fsearch/wiki/Database-update</a>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat féachaint go gníomhach ar fhillteáin aonair anois chun athscananna minice a dhíchur. Ansin feictear athruithe comhad i do thorthaí cuardaigh láithreach.\n"
"\n"
"Chun an ghné seo a chumasú téigh go dtí an roinn Bunachar Sonraí den dialóg Roghanna.\n"
"\n"
"Féach ar an doiciméadú ar líne le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais:\n"
"<a href=\\\"URL\\\">https://github.com/cboxdoerfer/fsearch/wiki/Database-update</a>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:323
msgid ""
"You can now use wildcards and regular expressions to define more powerful exclude rules. \n"
"Rules can be targeted specifically at files, folders, or both, and can be configured to match against either the basename or the full absolute path."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat saoróga agus slonn rialta a úsáid anois chun rialacha eisiaimh níos cumhachtaí a shainiú. \n"
"Is féidir rialacha a dhíriú go sonrach ar chomhaid, ar fhillteáin, nó ar an dá cheann, agus is féidir iad a chumrú chun meaitseáil leis an mbunainm nó leis an gconair iomlán."

#: src/fsearch_window.c:784
msgid ""
"Sorting by <b>Type</b> can take a few seconds with many results.\n"
"\n"
"This sort order is not persistent, it will be reset when the search term changes."
msgstr ""
"Seans go dtógfaidh sórtáil de réir <b>Cineál</b> cúpla soicind agus go leor torthaí.\n"
"\n"
"Níl an t-ordú sórtála seo leanúnach, déanfar é a athshocrú nuair a athraíonn an téarma cuardaigh."

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.desktop.in.in:4 src/main.c:36
msgid "FSearch"
msgstr "FSearch"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.desktop.in.in:5
msgid "A file search application focusing on performance and advanced features"
msgstr "Feidhmchlár cuardaigh comhad a dhíríonn ar fheidhmíocht agus ar ghnéithe ardleibhéil"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.desktop.in.in:10
msgid "search;fsearch;files;folders;music;video;documents;find;tool;everything;"
msgstr "cuardaigh;fsearch;comhaid;fillteáin;ceol;físeán;cáipéisí;aimsigh;uirlis;gach rud;"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.desktop.in.in:12
msgid "File Search Utility"
msgstr "Uirlis Chuardaigh Comhad"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:8
msgid "A graphical file search application"
msgstr "Feidhmchlár grafach chun comhaid a chuardach"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid "FSearch helps you to find files and folders as easy and fast as possible. Just type a few letters and search results will appear almost instantly."
msgstr "Cabhraíonn FSearch leat comhaid agus fillteáin a aimsiú chomh héasca agus chomh tapa agus is féidir. Ní gá ach cúpla litir a chlóscríobh agus taispeánfar torthaí an chuardaigh beagnach láithreach."

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:14
msgid "There are a lot of features which make searching as efficient and powerful as possible. Such as:"
msgstr "Tá go leor gnéithe ann a fhágann an cuardach chomh héifeachtach agus chomh cumhachtach agus is féidir. Mar shampla:"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:19
msgid "Ignore case (e.g. searching for \"<code>fsearch</code>\" will match \"FSearch\" as well)"
msgstr "Neamhaird ar chás (m.sh. meaitseálfaidh cuardach ar “<code>fsearch</code>” le “FSearch” freisin)"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:20
msgid "Regular expressions"
msgstr "Sloinn rialta"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:21
msgid "Wildcard support"
msgstr "Tacaíocht do shaoróga"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:22
msgid "Filter support (e.g. only search for audio files)"
msgstr "Tacaíocht scagairí (m.sh. gan chuardach ach ar chomhaid fhuaime)"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:23
msgid "Exclude certain files and folders"
msgstr "Fág comhaid agus fillteáin áirithe as an áireamh"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:24
msgid "Fast sort by name, path, size, modification time and extension"
msgstr "Sórtáil thapa de réir ainm, conaire, méid, ama athraithe agus iarmhíre"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:26
msgid "<em>Note:</em> Due to Flatpak's sandboxing, FSearch can't find every file on your system."
msgstr "<em>Nóta:</em> De bharr bhosca gainimh Flatpak, ní féidir le FSearch gach comhad ar do chóras a aimsiú."

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:35
msgid "The default UI layout"
msgstr "Leagan amach réamhshocraithe an chomhéadain"

#: data/io.github.cboxdoerfer.FSearch.metainfo.xml.in:41
msgid "A layout more closely following GNOME HIGs"
msgstr "Leagan amach a leanann Treoirlínte Comhéadain Dhaonna GNOME níos dlúithe"

